## 3. How long do we retain your data?

| Category | Retention period |
|---|---|
| Contact form data | Up to 12 months after last contact |
| Client and invoice data | 7 years (Dutch tax retention obligation) |
| Website analytics data | Per Google Analytics retention settings (14 months) |
| Microsoft Clarity data | Per Microsoft Clarity retention policy (up to 13 months) |

After the retention period, your data is deleted or anonymised.

